      "kind": "bullet",
      "text": "Understanding how this table handles data—and how it fails—is critical for building a scalable membership platform.</p> <h2>The Architecture of <code>wp_usermeta</code></h2> <p>Like the post meta and term meta tables, <code>wp_usermeta</code> follows the Entity-Attribute-Value (EAV) model.",
